Keep out of the reach and sight of children.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 4, 1900, 'IME-9 Tablet'),
('calpol.png', '<h1>Calpol 500 MG Table</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Calpol 500 MG Tablet is used to temporarily relieve fever and mild to moderate pain such as muscle ache, headache, toothache, arthritis, and backache. </li>\r\n    <li>This medicine should be used with caution in patients with liver diseases due to the increased risk of severe adverse effects.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Calpol 500 MG Tablet is used to temporarily relieve fever and mild to moderate pain such as muscle ache, headache, toothache, arthritis, and backache.</li>\r\n    <li>This medicine should be used with caution in patients with liver diseases due to the increased risk of severe adverse effects.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ol>\r\n    <li>Fever</li>\r\n    <li> Headache</li>\r\n    <li> Muscle Pain</li>\r\n    <li> Menstrual Cramps</li>\r\n    <li> Post Immunization Pyrexia</li>\r\n    <li> Arthritis</li>\r\n   \r\n</ol>', '<p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>The pain relieving effect of this medicine can be observed within an hour of administration. For fever reduction, the time taken to show the effect is about 30 minutes.</li>\r\n        <li>The effect of this medicine lasts for an average duration of 4-6 hours.</li>\r\n        <li>Consumption of alcohol is not recommended during treatment with this medicine due to the increased risk of serious side effects such as severe gastrointestinal bleeding, dizziness, fatigue, weakness, rashes, nausea, joint pain, fever, jaundice, etc.</li>\r\n        <li>This medicine is not recommended for use in pregnant women unless necessary and the potential benefits outweigh the risks involved. This medicine is not known to cause any harm to the fetus, but should only be used after consulting with a doctor.</li>\r\n        <li>\r\n                This medicine is safe to use during breastfeeding. However, it is advised to consult your doctor before taking this medicine. Monitoring the infant for any undesired side effects like skin rashes or diarrhea while taking this medicine is advised.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</p>', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Nausea or Vomiting</li>\r\n    <li>Allergic skin reaction</li>\r\n    <li>Gastric / Mouth Ulcer</li>\r\n    <li>Anemia-RARE</li>\r\n    <li>Unusual bleeding or bruising</li>\r\n    <li>Fatigue</li>\r\n</ul>', 0, 5, 30, 'Calpol 500 MG'),
('Gelusil.png', '<h1>Gelusil</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Gelusil is a combination medicine used to treat heartburn, acid indigestion, upset stomach, and bloating caused by gas.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Descriptoin:\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Aluminum and magnesium are naturally occurring minerals. Aluminum hydroxide and magnesium hydroxide are antacids.</li>\r\n    <li>Simethicone allows gas bubbles in the stomach and intestines to come together more easily, which allows for easier passage of gas.</li>\r\n    <li>This medication works only on existing acid in the stomach.</li>\r\n    <li> It does not prevent acid production.</li>\r\n    <li> It may be used alone or with other medications that lower acid production (e.g., H2 blockers such as cimetidine/ranitidine and proton pump inhibitors such as omeprazole).</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ol>\r\n    <li>This medication is used to treat the symptoms of too much stomach acid such as stomach upset, heartburn, and acid indigestion.</li>\r\n    <li>It is also used to relieve symptoms of extra gas such as belching, bloating, and feelings of pressure/discomfort in the stomach/gut.</li>\r\n    <li> Simethicone helps break up gas bubbles in the gut. Aluminum and magnesium antacids work quickly to lower the acid in the stomach. Liquid antacids usually work faster/better than tablets or capsules.</li>\r\n</ol>', '<p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Before taking this product, tell your doctor or pharmacist if you are allergic to aluminum hydroxide; or to magnesium; or to simethicone; or if you have any other allergies. This product may contain inactive ingredients, which can cause allergic reactions or other problems. Talk to your pharmacist for more details.</li>\r\n    <li>\r\n            If you have any of the following health problems, consult your doctor or pharmacist before using this product: frequent alcohol use, severe loss of body water (dehydration/fluid restriction), kidney problems (including kidney stones).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</p>', '<ul>\r\n    <li>This medication can cause nausea, constipation, diarrhea, or headache. If these symptoms persist or become severe, notify your doctor.</li>\r\n    <li> If your doctor has directed you to use this medication, remember that he or she has judged that the benefit to you is greater than the risk of side effects. Many people using this medication do not have serious side effects.</li>\r\n    <li>The magnesium in this product can cause diarrhea. Using an antacid that contains only aluminum along with this product can help control diarrhea. The aluminum in this product can cause constipation. To minimize constipation, drink plenty of fluids and exercise. Diarrhea is more common with this product than constipation.</li>\r\n   \r\n</ul>\r\n', 0, 6, 70, 'Gelusil'),
('dart1.png', '<h1>Dart Tablet, Pack of 10</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Dart Tablet is used for Headache, Cephalalgia, Pain, Fever, Ache, Drowsiness, Fatigue, Orthostatic hypotension, Cerebral palsy, Febrility and other conditions. Dart Tablet may also be used for purposes not listed in this medication guide.</li>\r\n    <li>Dart Tablet works by stimulating the central nervous system; antagonizing the adenosine receptors; blocking the action of cyclooxygenase in the body</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Dart Tablet contains Acetaminophen, Caffeine and Propylphenazone as active ingredients.</li>\r\n    <li>Dart Tablet is used for Headache, Cephalalgia, Pain, Fever, Ache, Drowsiness, Fatigue, Orthostatic hypotension, Cerebral palsy, Febrility and other conditions. Dart Tablet may also be used for purposes not listed in this medication guide.</li>\r\n    <li>Dart Tablet works by stimulating the central nervous system; antagonizing the adenosine receptors; blocking the action of cyclooxygenase in the body</li>\r\n    <li>Dart Tablet - Composition and Active Ingredients</li>\r\n    <li>Dart Tablet is composed of the following active ingredients (salts)</li>\r\n    <li>Propylphenazone - Propypheanazone - 150 MG</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ol>\r\n    <li>Headache</li>\r\n    <li>Cephalalgia</li>\r\n    <li>Pain</li>\r\n    <li>Fever</li>\r\n    <li>Ache</li>\r\n    <li>Drowsiness</li>\r\n    <li>Fatigue</li>\r\n    <li>Orthostatic hypotension</li>\r\n    <li>Bronchopulmonary dysplasia in premature infants</li>\r\n</ol>', '<p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Avoid exposing medication to excessive heat</li>\r\n        <li>Consume the medicine only at recommended doses</li>\r\n        <li>Do not exceed 4, 000 mg daily dose in adults</li>\r\n        <li>Do not take =3 alcoholic drinks per day while taking Acetaminophen</li>\r\n        <li>Do not use with other drugs containing Acetaminophen</li>\r\n\r\n    </ul>\r\n</p>', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Gastric acid secretion</li>\r\n    <li>Agitation</li>\r\n    <li>Gastrointestinal problems</li>\r\n    <li>Skin reactions</li>\r\n    <li>Dermatological reactions</li>\r\n    <li>Restlessness</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 1, 7, 42, 'Dart'),
('homeo1.png\r\n', '<h1>Dr. Reckeweg Calcarea Phosphorica Biochemic Tablet 6X</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Calcarea Phos 6X Tablet is a bone and teeth supplement, it is a homeopathic medicine.</li>\r\n    <li>It is commonly prescribed for teething problems in infants, after dental drilling or surgery, to reduce tooth decay, and to stimulate the timely eruption of teeth.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n    <li>An insufficient supply of calcarea phosphoricum can result in deficient nutrition and retarded growth, thus it is often needed during puberty to encourage normal growth and development.</li>\r\n    <li> In the same way Calc phos can be helpful to prevent fractures and reduce osteoporotic tendencies in the elderly. Cell salts work well together when combined. </li>\r\n    <li>For delayed dentition in children (teeth are erupting too slowly or late), Calc fluor, Calc phos, and Silicea are often prescribed together. </li>\r\n    <li>To restore the body after major acute illnesses and to treat fatigue and anemia, Calc phos and Ferrum phos are often taken together. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', ' <ol>\r\n     <li>Infant- 2 Tablets 2 times a day</li>\r\n     <li>Children- 2 Tablets 4 times a day; </li>\r\n     <li>Adults- 4 Tablets 4 times a day</li>\r\n </ol>\r\n', '<p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>And since Mag phos helps harden dental enamel, it is often combined with Calc fluor, Calc phos, and/or Silicea post-dental drilling or surgery. \r\n            Additionally, Calc phos and Mag phos are often prescribed in combination to treat muscle or menstrual cramps and spasms. \r\n            </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</p>', 'None', 1, 8, 320, 'Dr. Reckeweg Calcarea Phosphorica Biochemic Tablet 6X'),
('homeo2.png', '<h1>SBL Scalptone Tablet</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Scalptone is used for excessive hair loss can be caused by dandruff, genetic factors, diseases, stress, medications, under or over activity of sebaceous glands and ageing.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Scalptone is a combination of well proven drugs of homoeopathic therapeutics to keep hair roots healthy and prevent hair-loss.</li>\r\n        <li>Scalptone is used for excessive hair loss can be caused by dandruff, genetic factors, diseases, stress, medications, under or over activity of sebaceous glands and ageing.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<ol>\r\n    <li>Scalptone is a combination of well proven drugs of homoeopathic therapeutics to keep hair roots healthy and prevent hair-loss.</li>\r\n    <li>\r\n        Scalptone is used for excessive hair loss can be caused by dandruff, genetic factors, diseases, stress, medications, under or over activity of sebaceous glands and ageing.\r\n    </li>\r\n</ol>', '<p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n        <li>Adults: 4 tablets, 4-6 times daily.</li>\r\n        <li>Children: Half of the adults dose.</li>\r\n        <li>Use under medical supervision.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</p>', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Acidum fluoricum 3x</li>\r\n    <li>Natrum muriaticum 3x</li>\r\n    <li>Calcarea phosphorica 3x</li>\r\n    <li>Badiaga 3x</li>\r\n</ul>', 0, 9, 230, 'SBL Scalptone Tablet'),
